
* Conda Environment: conda create -n gpu_glm python=3.12 -y
* Delete Environment: conda env remove -n gpu_glm
* Install system dependancies: 
*  conda install -c nvidia cuda-runtime=12.4 -n gpu_glm -y
*  conda install -n gpu_glm -c conda-forge cupy -y
* Activate Conda: conda activate gpu_glm
* Deactivate Conda: conda deactivate
* Install build: pip install build
* Install twine: pip install twine
* Build: python -m build
* Install: pip install .
* Install Dev: pip install -e .[dev]
* Uninstall: pip uninstall gpu_glm -y
* Style: ruff format .
* Lint: ruff check . --fix
* Pre-commit check: pre-commit run --all-files
* Test: pytest -v
* Document: mkdocs build --strict
* Serve documentation: mkdocs serve
* symlink index.md and README: ln -s docs/index.md README.md

